Level Edit Revisions

A system of windows for editing.
First window is the window where all of the objects can be seen and moved and stuff. (Add/Delete Mode)
Second window is the information about that object. (Select Mode)
Third window is the specific information about that object. (Object specific mode)
Fourth window is the information about the world. (Background, tiles, object amount, terrain)
Fifth window is the File information. (File Mode)

Extra window used for file loading, texture finding, texture loading, color picker.
Takes place of first window.

All other windows are on the right and are sub sections of each other separated by tabs.